paragraphs.title: Load data from s3 into Spark DF
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.spark
val sensorDF = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", "true").option("mode", "DROPMALFORMED").option("inferSchema", "true").option("delimiter", ",").load("s3a://sunileman1/phm_data_challenge/tsdata/")
val faultDF = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", "true").option("mode", "DROPMALFORMED").option("inferSchema", "true").option("delimiter", ",").load("s3a://sunileman1/phm_data_challenge/faults/")

sensorDF.createOrReplaceTempView("sensorDF")
faultDF.createOrReplaceTempView("faultDF")

paragraphs.title: Inner join on tool and time
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.spark

val matchedDF = sensorDF.join(faultDF, sensorDF("Tool") === faultDF("Tool") && sensorDF("time") === faultDF("time") , joinType="inner").drop(faultDF("Tool")).drop(faultDF("time"))

matchedDF.createOrReplaceTempView("matchedDF")
